---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import hiroshimaImg from '../assets/hiroshima.png';
import ggjBanner from '../assets/ggj26_banner.png';
import unityMokumokuBanner from '../assets/mokumoku_banner.png';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<Layout title="広島Unity勉強会へようこそ！">
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>広島でUnityを!<br />楽しく学んでいくコミュニティ</h1>
			<p class="hero-description">
				初心者からプロまで、ゲーム開発やXR技術に興味がある仲間が集まり、<br>交流しながらスキルを高め合う地域密着型の <strong><i class="fa-brands fa-unity"></i>&nbsp;Unityコミュニティ</strong> です。
			</p>
			<div class="hero-buttons">
				<a href="https://hirouni.connpass.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
					<i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i> イベントに参加する
				</a>
				<a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary-outline">
					活動について詳しく <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="activities">
		<h2 class="section-title">主な活動内容</h2>
		<div class="activity-grid">
			<div class="activity-card">
				<div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i></div>
				<h3>もくもく会</h3>
				<p>各自の作業を進めるためのサードプレイス。雑談、分からないところを教え合ったりします。</p>
			</div>
			<div class="activity-card">
				<div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user"></i></div>
				<h3>セミナー・講座</h3>
				<p>Unityに関する様々なテーマで学習します。初学者および開発者向けのハンズオンも開催しています。</p>
			</div>
			<div class="activity-card">
				<div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-gamepad"></i></div>
				<h3>ゲームジャム</h3>
				<p>短期間で集中してゲームを制作するイベントです。チーム開発の楽しさ、一本のゲームを完成させる体験を。</p>
			</div>
			<div class="activity-card">
				<div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i></div>
				<h3>技術・交流会</h3>
				<p>Unityや素材作成、XR技術など、幅広いテーマで情報交換や相談を行っています。</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="latest-info">
		<div class="info-card">
			<h2 class="section-title">最新情報</h2>
			
			<div class="special-event">
				<a href="https://hirouni.connpass.com/event/383865/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="top-banner-link">
					<Image src={unityMokumokuBanner} alt="Unityもくもく会" class="top-banner-img" />
				</a>
				<p>3月8日(日)Unityもくもく会開催決定。みんなでUnityやGodotでゲームを作ろう！ <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></p>
			</div>

			<div class="special-event">
				<a href="https://globalgamejam.org/group/31042/games" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="top-banner-link">
					<Image src={ggjBanner} alt="Global Game Jam 2026 Hiroshima" class="top-banner-img" />
				</a>
				<p>GGJ2026広島で作成したゲームを公開中。ここからレッツプレイ！ <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></p>
			</div>

			<p>最新のイベント情報の掲載や参加申し込みは、connpassで行っています。<br>ぜひグループをフォローしてください！</p>
			<a href="https://hirouni.connpass.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="connpass-banner">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt"></i> 広島Unity勉強会 connpassページ
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.hero {
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(179, 11, 84, 0.9) 0%, rgba(255, 77, 148, 0.8) 100%), url(/src/assets/hiroshima.png);
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		background-blend-mode: multiply;
		border-radius: 12px;
		color: white;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	/* Fallback for environments where the image path might differ */
	.hero {
		background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(179, 11, 84, 0.9) 0%, rgba(255, 77, 148, 0.8) 100%), url('../assets/hiroshima.png');
	}
	.hero-content h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}
	.hero-description {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}
	.hero-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	/* Buttons */
	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s;
	}
	.btn-primary {
		background-color: white;
		color: #b30b54;
	}
	.btn-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
	}
	.btn-secondary-outline {
		background-color: transparent;
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid white;
	}
	.btn-secondary-outline:hover {
		background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
	}

	/* Sections */
	.section-title {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		border-bottom: none;
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.section-title::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 50px;
		height: 3px;
		background-color: #b30b54;
	}

	/* Activity Grid */
	.activity-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}
	.activity-card {
		background: #f8f9fa;
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		transition: transform 0.2s;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.activity-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		background: white;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
	}
	.icon-wrapper {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: #b30b54;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.activity-card h3 {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}
	.activity-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* Latest Info */
	.latest-info {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	.info-card {
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		background: white;
		border: 1px solid #eee;
		border-radius: 12px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	/* Special Event Banner */
	.special-event {
		margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		overflow: hidden;
		box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
	}
	.special-event:hover {
		transform: scale(1.02);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
	}
	.top-banner-link {
		display: block;
		position: relative;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.top-banner-img {
		width: 100%;
		height: auto;
		display: block;
	}
	.banner-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.7));
		color: white;
		padding: 2rem 1rem 1rem;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.3s;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: flex-end;
	}
	.top-banner-link:hover .banner-overlay {
		opacity: 1;
	}
	.banner-overlay span {
		background: #b30b54;
		padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	.connpass-banner {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		background-color: #d31d00;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		transition: background-color 0.2s;
	}
	.connpass-banner:hover {
		background-color: #2980b9;
	}

	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.hero {
			padding: 3rem 1rem;
		}
		.hero-content h1 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
		}
		.activity-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.banner-overlay {
			opacity: 1;
			padding: 1rem;
			background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
		}
	}
</style>


